formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
Details of Annexure 3A of Form 3 has not been verified by us.  Same has ben provided on the basis of information provided by the promoter of the project.  Details of Form 3 has been provided on the basis of information of accounting data provided by the promoter.
 There are many expenses for which phase wise details from books of accounts is not available, so we have relied on the details received from the client for expenses incurred.  Cost incurred for specific phase has been taken on the basis of Engineer Certificate and creditors for the same has been deducted from the same to arrive figure of cost incurred and paid for specific phase.

Total unsecured loan  has been taken by promoter for a company as a whole and usage of same is mixed for all project so project wise unsecured loan bifurcation is not possible.
